The '''Battery Farm''' somehow grows [[en/Manual/Base Set/Cargos/Batteries]]. Its space requirement is equal to that of a [[en/Manual/Base Set/Industries/Forest]] in temperate/sub-artic climates or plantations in sub-tropic climates.

Batteries can be transported to a [[en/Manual/Base Set/Industries/Toy Factory|Toy Factory]] to help produce toys.

